HEARTWATER, IMPORTED - USA (FLORIDA) (02)
*********************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
See Also
Heartwater, imported - USA (Florida): alert 20000105131456
Heartwater, imported - USA (Florida): ticks wanted 20000109133946
[1
Date: Sun, 09 Jan 2000 07:49:41 -0500
From: "Dr. L. G. Clark" <lclark@globe-net.net>

Dr. E. H. Doten and I warned of the unrestricted importation of
Amblyomma-infested reptiles through the Miami International Airport in
1995 (Proc.Vet. Epi. Econ Symp., Austin, TX May 31-June2, 1995) and
urged federal and state authorities to institute some form of inspection
and/or control.
--
L. G. Clark DVM
2722 Padden Court
